reviews.text: Get the goose and suckling pig with gai lan - sorted. 670 HKD with two beers and rice.
Our HK friend took us here and it was mostly  empty inside so we were apprehensive  whether it would be good or not. He ordered the goose, pork skin, and clams. Definitely recommend.
The dim sums are pretty good. Tasty and well presented
Good food good service

Great food in general not much MSG, some traditional dishes that are difficult to find in most restaurants.  Service is good, price is a bit on the high side, very nice environment for gathering, chat and drink.  Close a bit early at 11:30 in the busy area

result.name: 新斗記

reviews.text: 服務員態度非常差👎
超贊👍👍👍

之前已來過幾次，今天星期六來幫襯，不用輪候位置，顧客不太多！
燒鵝皮脆肉香不肥膩，味道不錯！
香煎蓮藕餅內裏蓮藕爽脆，配上豬肉一起絞碎香煎，口感特別！
蝦仁炒蛋十分足料，滑蛋配上大大粒蝦仁，性價比高！
豆豉雞煲就比較油，不太值得吃！
通菜炒牛肉的通菜新鮮，牛肉嫩滑有鑊氣！
瑤柱蛋白炒飯有炒工，每粒白飯分明又太油，值得推介！
整體來說這一次一家大細五位，結帳也只是剛剛$1000左右，在尖沙咀這個地區的價錢十分超值！
叉燒肉好吃，但是切太大塊了吧，一片底4口。
